Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.61,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H8B87D7&}答案是什么我依然没有猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:14.03,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H4C9FD6&}只知道有了感觉就向前冲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:15.33,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H83624A&}接着走
